      <section eId="sec_CC-564">
        <num>CC 564</num>
        <heading>564.  Treasure</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 564.  Treasure.
The usufructuary has no right to the enjoyment of a treasure found in the property of which he has the usufruct.  If the usufructuary has found the treasure, he is entitled to keep one-half of it as finder.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110753</p>
        </authorialNote>
